


Montreux-Palace Hotel

1820 Montreux, Switzerland

December 26, 1973

Dear Professor Ackermann,

My husband asks me to reply to your letter of December 10, as he is too intensely occupied with the novel he is writing to be able to interrupt his work.

He thanks you for your kind offer to prepublish part of his collection of lectures in the Boston University Journal. It would be, however, premature to discuss this as he has several other projects that must be dealt with before comes the turn o